results.occurrenceRemarks: Here we can see the key ID features that distinguish this rare tropicbird (rare at least on Little Tobago) from its relative, the red billed (www.flickr.com/photos/68961563@N02/13008772773/in/photost...) Note that rather than having black barring on its back, this species sports a "V" pattern that starts on its wings and goes onto its back. Also, the bill color here is yellow, rather than red.
